social_posts.post_text: Thank you so much @lisa_lynette68 for making our annual Christmas party such a pretty, festive and fun night!!! We all had a blast and enjoyed the yummy taco soup, goodies, hot cocoa, Rumchata (we definitely will be buying a large bottle next time!!) & loved all the beautiful Christmas decorations. Can’t wait til next year’s!

Robert Bryan Perrin and Amanda Perrin Rustic Pines Retreat is listed live https://ruidosoreservations.com and just in time for Spring/Summer!! If you want a close by destination to relax, enjoy family time, beautiful weather, great cuisine and fun shopping you should look at their listing. Let me know if you have any questions.

Congratulations to my nephew and niece!! They graduated from University of Arkansas last weekend. We are so proud of them and their hard work. They planned their wedding, worked and still graduated on time. So happy we could be there to celebrate your accomplishment! Love you both. So happy you are coming back to Texas!!
#collagegraduate #hardworkpaysoffs #Texas #universityofarkansas #graduation #couplegoals

New updated photos of my son and daughter’s Ruidoso vacation home are up on Ruidosoreservations.com and the listing is Rustic Pines Retreat.  If you are from the Carlsbad area and visit  Ruidoso or have family and friends who enjoy visiting there please feel free to share!! Or if you need an escape from the heat this summer than you will love the great mild temps during the day and the cool nights. I can’t wait for our trip there later this summer!! Looking forward to the great restaurants, shopping and relaxing. You can follow the link below to look at available dates. 

https://ruidosoreservations.com/property/19b0c8c3-0c89-486f-a659-9bf2820ead23

#newmexico #ruidosonewmexico #ruidoso #mountainvacation #mountainretreat #newmexicotravel

It was such a fun night! Several of our JWC team were able to attend the 2023 Annual Awards Banquet for the Southlake Chamber of Commerce.  Jason and Jaime Webber were not able to make it last evening so they invited us to attend and enjoy a fun evening, great company, a fabulous dinner. We were able to help recognize & support our community and the individuals who were recognized for their community contributions this past year. @southlakechamber did a phenomenal job on the awards banquet!! @jwconstructiongroup

Anniversary dinner with my hubby at Perry’s.  33 Years with this man and I love him more everyday!!

It was a relaxing drive from Ruidoso NM to White Sands National Park. Beautiful white sands and some fun in the sun! Next time we will know to buy the wax for our sleds.
